---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-20">
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">Who We Are</h1>
      <div class="prose prose-lg">
        <p>
          At Q10 Labs, we specialize in delivering AI-driven solutions to small and medium-sized 
          enterprises (SMEs). Our focus is on developing Minimum Viable Products (MVPs) that enable 
          businesses to test, validate, and scale AI initiatives with minimal risk and maximum impact.
        </p>
        <p>
          With deep expertise in data science, software engineering, and business consulting, 
          we create scalable AI models that optimize business processes, improve efficiency, 
          and reduce costs. We are committed to delivering value quickly, guiding clients from 
          concept to execution while maintaining full control over the development process to 
          ensure the highest quality.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">Who We Work With</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg">
        <p>
          We work with SMEs across various industries, including logistics, finance, healthcare, 
          and management. Our ideal clients are those who:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Are looking to implement AI solutions but lack the in-house expertise to design and deploy them</li>
          <li>Want to optimize their operations using data-driven insights</li>
          <li>Need a partner who can guide them through the AI implementation journey</li>
          <li>Value rapid prototyping and iterative development</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>